title: Jocko Podcast 24 with Jody Mitic - "Unflinching"
description:
Join the conversation on Twitter: @jockowillink @JODYMITIC @echocharles

Jocko reviews excerpts from Canadian Sniper, Afganistan Vet, and Ottawa (CANADA) City Councilman, Jody Mitic's book, "Unflinching" with personal, in-depth commentary from Jody himself.
